text: Wanna One () was a South Korean boy band, formed in 2017 through the second season of the talent show Produce 101. They worked under YMC Entertainment. It consists of eleven members: Kang Daniel, Park Ji-hoon, Lee Dae-hwi, Kim Jae- hwan, Ong Seong-wu, Park Woo-jin, Lai Kuan-lin, Yoon Ji-sung, Hwang Min-hyun, Bae Jin-young and Ha Sung-woon.
